## Database Directory

```
db/
├── migrate/                   # All migrations (timestamped)
│   ├── 20251103120000_create_users.rb
│   ├── 20251103120001_create_articles.rb
│   └── 20251103120002_add_published_to_articles.rb
├── schema.rb                  # Current schema (auto-generated)
└── seeds.rb                   # Seed data for development
```

**Rules:**
- Never edit `schema.rb` directly
- Never delete old migrations
- Use descriptive migration names
- Keep migrations focused (one change per migration)

